Body: What is Educoin Online Learning Platform? Educoin is the Learning Platform of the future powered by the blockchain  While existing solutions offer to solve just one problem at a time, our team is up to build a secure, powerful, & global learning platform on the stability of ERC20 blockchain payment technology.
